long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TrackerR is a convenient extension for time and productivity tracking. It lets you log time spent on different tasks and projects, view a history of your activity to track progress, earn achievements for reaching goals, and analyze time statistics to identify areas for improvement. TrackerR is your personal assistant for boosting productivity and self-discipline.
